---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Cloud Identity Summit 2020">
    <main class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 py-20 w-full flex-grow">
        
        <div class="mb-12">
            <a href="/archive" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-blue-500 hover:text-blue-400 text-sm font-semibold transition bg-slate-900/50 border border-slate-800 px-4 py-2 rounded-lg">
                ← Back to Archive
            </a>
        </div>

        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold text-white tracking-tight mb-8">
            Cloud Identity Summit 2020
        </h1>

        <div class="text-slate-300 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-16 space-y-6">
            <p>The first Cloud Identity Summit took place on October 23, 2020. Originally planned as an on-site conference in Koblenz, the event was held as a virtual conference due to the pandemic. Seven sessions were offered in two tracks.</p>
        </div>

        <section class="mb-20">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-8 border-b border-slate-800 pb-4">Agenda & Speakers</h2>
            
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
                <div class="bg-slate-900/50 p-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-800 hover:border-slate-700 transition flex flex-col">
                    <span class="text-blue-400 text-sm font-mono block mb-2">Level 300</span>
                    <strong class="text-white block mb-3 text-xl">Azure AD Sync – backbone of hybrid setup</strong>
                    <p class="text-sm text-slate-400 mb-4 flex-grow">Synchronization is a very important topic in an hybrid environment. Join the session to discuss and learn along the most important topics in every customer hybrid scenario.</p>
                    <div class="pt-4 border-t border-slate-800/50 mt-auto">
                        <span class="text-slate-200 font-semibold block">Klaus Bierschenk</span>
                        <span class="text-slate-500 text-sm">Solution Architect (cellent GmbH)</span>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="bg-slate-900/50 p-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-800 hover:border-slate-700 transition flex flex-col">
                    <span class="text-blue-400 text-sm font-mono block mb-2">Level 300</span>
                    <strong class="text-white block mb-3 text-xl">Identity Protection: Deep Dive, find what you usually do not see</strong>
                    <div class="pt-4 border-t border-slate-800/50 mt-auto">
                        <span class="text-slate-200 font-semibold block">Thomas Detzner</span>
                        <span class="text-slate-500 text-sm">Senior Program Manager (Microsoft)</span>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="bg-slate-900/50 p-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-800 hover:border-slate-700 transition flex flex-col">
                    <strong class="text-white block mb-3 text-xl mt-4">Azure AD B2B: Notes from the field</strong>
                    <div class="pt-4 border-t border-slate-800/50 mt-auto">
                        <span class="text-slate-200 font-semibold block">Stephan Wälde</span>
                        <span class="text-slate-500 text-sm">Lead Cloud Architect (Glück & Kanja)</span>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="bg-slate-900/50 p-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-800 hover:border-slate-700 transition flex flex-col">
                    <span class="text-blue-400 text-sm font-mono block mb-2">Level 300</span>
                    <strong class="text-white block mb-3 text-xl">Building a passwordless World</strong>
                    <p class="text-sm text-slate-400 mb-4 flex-grow">Passwords are the weakest link for security and your business. Come learn how you can incorporate password-less authentication into your MFA strategy and provide secure authentication to your end users during this demo packed session.</p>
                    <div class="pt-4 border-t border-slate-800/50 mt-auto">
                        <span class="text-slate-200 font-semibold block">Stefan van der Wiele</span>
                        <span class="text-slate-500 text-sm">Senior Program Manager (Microsoft)</span>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="bg-slate-900/50 p-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-800 hover:border-slate-700 transition flex flex-col">
                    <span class="text-yellow-500 text-sm font-mono block mb-2">Sponsor Session (Level 300)</span>
                    <strong class="text-white block mb-3 text-xl">How Yubico technical designs FIDO2 authentication</strong>
                    <div class="pt-4 border-t border-slate-800/50 mt-auto">
                        <span class="text-slate-200 font-semibold block">Jan M. Quack</span>
                        <span class="text-slate-500 text-sm">Senior Solution Engineer (Yubico)</span>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="bg-slate-900/50 p-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-800 hover:border-slate-700 transition flex flex-col">
                    <strong class="text-white block mb-3 text-xl mt-4">Manage identity lifecycle and access control with Azure AD Identity Governance</strong>
                    <div class="pt-4 border-t border-slate-800/50 mt-auto">
                        <span class="text-slate-200 font-semibold block">Jan Vidar Elven</span>
                        <span class="text-slate-500 text-sm">Architect (Skill AS)</span>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="bg-slate-900/50 p-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-800 hover:border-slate-700 transition flex flex-col">
                    <strong class="text-white block mb-3 text-xl mt-4">AADInternals - Building a hacking tool</strong>
                    <p class="text-sm text-slate-400 mb-4 flex-grow">AAD Internals is a PowerShell module where I've tried to put all the knowledge I've gained during the years spent with Office 365 and Azure AD.</p>
                    <div class="pt-4 border-t border-slate-800/50 mt-auto">
                        <span class="text-slate-200 font-semibold block">Dr. Nestori Syynimaa</span>
                        <span class="text-slate-500 text-sm">Infosec researcher (Gerenios Ltd)</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>
</Layout>